"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Orders` and remove "
"the :guilabel:`Confirmed` filter. Then, open the :icon:`fa-caret-down` "
"dropdown menu and, under :guilabel:`Filters`, select :guilabel:`Unpaid`."
msgstr ""
"Pour afficher uniquement les commandes à l'étape :guilabel:`Devis envoyé`, "
"aller à :menuselection:`Site Web --> eCommerce --> Commandes` et retirer le "
"filtre :guilabel:`Confirmé`. Ensuite, ouvrir le menu déroulant :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` et, sous :guilabel:`Filtres`, sélectionner :guilabel:`Impayé`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:42
msgid ""
"E-commerce orders can be automatically assigned to a specific sales team or "
"salesperson. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, under :guilabel:`Orders "
"Assignment`, select the relevant :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"or :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"Les commandes e-commerce peuvent être automatiquement attribuées à une "
"équipe commerciale ou un vendeur spécifique. Pour ce faire, aller à "
":menuselection:`Site Web --> Configuration --> Paramètres`. Dans la section "
":guilabel:`eCommerce`, sous :guilabel:`Attribution des commandes`, "
"sélectionner l':guilabel:`Équipe commerciale` ou le :guilabel:`Vendeur` "
"concerné."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:48
msgid ""
"This three-step process is not visible to customers. However, they can view "
"their orders and check their status through the customer :doc:`portal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>`."
msgstr ""
"Ce processus en trois étapes n'est pas visible pour les clients. Cependant, "
"ils peuvent consulter leurs commandes et vérifier leur statut via le "
":doc:`portail </applications/general/users/user_portals>` client."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/order_handling.rst:51
msgid ""
"If the customer pays via :ref:`wire transfer <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, the quotation is *not* automatically "
"confirmed. In this case, the customer receives a notification on "
"the :guilabel:`My account` page of their :doc:`customer account "
"<configuration/customer_accounts>` to review and pay for the order. After "
"the payment is received, the order must be manually confirmed in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Si le client paie par :ref:`virement bancaire <payment_providers/"
"bank_payments/wire_transfer>`, le devis n'est *pas* confirmé "
"automatiquement. Dans ce cas, le client reçoit une notification sur la page "
":guilabel:`Mon compte` de son :doc:`compte client <configuration/"
"customer_accounts>` pour consulter et payer la commande. Après réception du "
"paiement, la commande doit être confirmée manuellement dans le backend."

