#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:37
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`New Providers` page, click the :guilabel:`Delivery "
"methods` button of an already-installed provider to access the delivery "
"method's form, or :guilabel:`Install` a new provider."
msgstr ""
"Sur la page :guilabel:`nouveaux prestataires`, cliquer sur le bouton "
":guilabel:`méthodes de livraison` d'un prestataire déjà installé pour "
"accéder au formulaire de la méthode de livraison, ou :guilabel:`installer` "
"un nouveau prestataire."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:40
msgid ""
":doc:`Configure the delivery method </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Configurer la méthode de livraison </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/third_party_shipper>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:44
msgid ""
"The :ref:`shipping price <inventory/shipping/calculate-delivery-cost>`, "
"including the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` or :guilabel:`Additional margin` "
"configured on the :ref:`delivery method <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"configure-delivery-method>` (if applicable), is displayed when selecting the "
"provider during :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`."
msgstr ""
"Le :ref:`prix d'expédition <inventory/shipping/calculate-delivery-cost>`, "
"incluant la :guilabel:`marge sur tarif` ou la :guilabel:`marge "
"supplémentaire` configurée sur la :ref:`méthode de livraison <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/configure-delivery-method>` (le cas échéant), s'affiche "
"lors de la sélection du prestataire pendant la :ref:`commande <ecommerce/"
"checkout/steps>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:50
msgid ""
"It is also possible to connect your e-commerce to shipping aggregators, such "
"as :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping>` "
"or :doc:`Envia.com </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping>`, or to fulfillment "
"platforms like :doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/gelato>`."
msgstr ""
"Il est également possible de connecter votre e-commerce à des agrégateurs "
"d'expédition, tels que :doc:`Sendcloud </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping>` ou "
":doc:`Envia.com </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/envia_shipping>`, ou à des "
"plateformes de fulfillment comme :doc:`Gelato </applications/sales/sales/"
"gelato>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:59
