#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:64
msgid "to configure shipping :ref:`based on rules <inventory/shipping/rules>`;"
msgstr ""
"pour configurer une livraison :ref:`basée sur des règles <inventory/shipping/"
