#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo allows you to :ref:`create <website/pages/page_creation>` different "
"kinds of webpages, including with the help of :ref:`AI <website/pages/ai-"
"generator>`, :ref:`publish <website/pages/un-publish-page>` them, and define "
"their structure and visibility by configuring :ref:`page properties <website/"
"pages/page_properties>`. Pages can be :ref:`duplicated <website/pages/"
"duplicate-page>`, :ref:`deleted <website/pages/delete-page>`, "
"and :ref:`redirected <website/pages/URL-redirection>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo permet de :ref:`créer <website/pages/page_creation>` différents types "
"de pages web, y compris avec l'aide de l':ref:`IA <website/pages/ai-"
"generator>`, de les :ref:`publier <website/pages/un-publish-page>`, et de "
"définir leur structure et visibilité en configurant les :ref:`propriétés de "
"page <website/pages/page_properties>`. Les pages peuvent être "
":ref:`dupliquées <website/pages/duplicate-page>`, :ref:`supprimées <website/"
"pages/delete-page>`, et :ref:`redirigées <website/pages/URL-redirection>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:16
msgid "Page types"
msgstr "Types de pages"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Static** pages, such as the homepage or :ref:`custom <website/pages/"
"page_creation>` pages, contain fixed content that does not change "
"dynamically. You can manually create these pages, define their URLs, and "
"adapt their :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_properties>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Les pages **statiques**, telles que la page d'accueil ou les pages "
":ref:`personnalisées <website/pages/page_creation>`, contiennent un contenu "
"fixe qui ne change pas dynamiquement. Ces pages peuvent être créées "
"manuellement, leurs URL définies, et leurs :ref:`propriétés <website/pages/"
"page_properties>` adaptées selon les besoins."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Dynamic** pages, on the other hand, display content that changes "
"automatically based on the data in the database and user interaction (e.g., "
"filtering). They are generated automatically by Odoo, for example, when "
"installing an app or module (e.g., `/shop` or `/blog`) or publishing a "
"new :doc:`product <../../ecommerce>` or :doc:`blog post <../../blog>`. "
"Dynamic pages are managed differently from static pages."
msgstr ""
"Les pages **dynamiques**, en revanche, affichent un contenu qui change "
"automatiquement en fonction des données de la base de données et de "
"l'interaction de l'utilisateur (par ex., filtrage). Elles sont générées "
"automatiquement par Odoo, par exemple lors de l'installation d'une "
"application ou d'un module (par ex., `/shop` ou `/blog`) ou de la "
"publication d'un nouveau :doc:`produit <../../ecommerce>` ou :doc:`article "
"de blog <../../blog>`. Les pages dynamiques sont gérées différemment des "
"pages statiques."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:31
msgid "Page creation"
msgstr "Création de pages"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:33
msgid "Website pages can be created from the **frontend** and the **backend**."
msgstr ""
"Les pages de site web peuvent être créées depuis le **frontend** et le "
"**backend**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:35
msgid "To create a new website page:"
msgstr "Créer une nouvelle page de site web :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:37
msgid ""
"Either open the **Website** app, click :guilabel:`New` :icon:`fa-caret-down` "
"in the top-right corner, then select :guilabel:`Page`;"
msgstr ""
"Ouvrez l'application **Site Web**, cliquez sur :guilabel:`Nouveau` :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` dans le coin supérieur droit, puis sélectionnez :guilabel:`Page` "
";"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:39
msgid ""
"Or go to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Ou allez à :menuselection:`Site Web --> Site --> Pages` et cliquez sur "
":guilabel:`Nouveau`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:41
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up, select a template. Templates are grouped "
"by type:"
msgstr ""
"Dans la fenêtre contextuelle :guilabel:`Nouvelle page`, sélectionnez un "
"modèle. Les modèles sont regroupés par type :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Basic`: Multi-purpose page. A blank page is also available to "
"start from scratch."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Basique` : page polyvalente. Une page vierge est également "
"disponible pour commencer de zéro."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`About`: Information about the brand and company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`À propos` : informations sur la marque et l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Landing Pages`: Summary of company content and information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pages de destination` : résumé du contenu et des informations de "
"l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`Gallery`: Photos and media showcase."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Galerie` : vitrine de photos et médias."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:47
msgid ":guilabel:`Services`: Overview of the services offered by the company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Services` : aperçu des services offerts par l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:48
msgid ":guilabel:`Pricing Plans`: Overview of the subscriptions and prices."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Plans tarifaires` : aperçu des abonnements et des prix."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Team`: The people behind the company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Équipe` : les personnes derrière l'entreprise."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Custom`: Custom-created templates. To add a custom template, open "
"the page you want to save as a template and :ref:`edit the page's properties "
"<website/pages/page_properties>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Personnalisé` : modèles créés sur mesure. Pour ajouter un modèle "
"personnalisé, ouvrez la page que vous souhaitez enregistrer comme modèle et "
":ref:`modifiez les propriétés de la page <website/pages/page_properties>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:54
msgid "In the :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up:"
msgstr "Dans la fenêtre contextuelle :guilabel:`Nouvelle page` :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:56
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Page Title`. This title is used in the menu and the "
"page's URL."
msgstr ""
"Saisissez un :guilabel:`Titre de page`. Ce titre est utilisé dans le menu et "
"l'URL de la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:57
msgid ""
"Disable :guilabel:`Add to menu` if the page should not appear in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Désactivez l'option :guilabel:`Ajouter au menu` si la page ne doit pas "
"figurer dans le menu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:58
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Generate text` to use the :ref:`AI <website/pages/ai-"
"generator>` tool to build the page."
msgstr ""
"Activez :guilabel:`Générer du texte` pour utiliser l'outil :ref:`IA <website/"
"pages/ai-generator>` afin de créer la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:62
msgid ""
"If needed, :doc:`customize the page's content and appearance <../"
"web_design>` using the website editor or :ref:`translate <translate/"
"translate>` it, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Si nécessaire, :doc:`personnalisez le contenu et l'apparence de la page <../"
"web_design>` à l'aide de l'éditeur de site web ou :ref:`traduisez <translate/"
"translate>` la page, puis cliquez sur :guilabel:`Enregistrer`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:64
msgid ":ref:`Publish <website/pages/un-publish-page>` the page."
msgstr ":ref:`Publier <website/pages/un-publish-page>` la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:69
msgid "AI webpage generator"
msgstr "Générateur de page web IA"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:71
msgid ""
"To generate content using AI when :ref:`creating a new page <website/pages/"
"page_creation>`, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Pour générer du contenu à l'aide de l'IA lors de la :ref:`création d'une "
"nouvelle page <website/pages/page_creation>`, suivez ces étapes :"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:74
msgid ""
"After choosing a template, in the :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up, toggle "
"the :guilabel:`AI Generate Text` switch."
msgstr ""
"Après avoir choisi un modèle, dans la fenêtre contextuelle "
":guilabel:`Nouvelle page`, activez le bouton :guilabel:`Générer du texte "
"avec l'IA`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:76
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Instructions` field, enter a short description of the page "
"being created. This should include a few important keywords that define the "
"page's focus and scope."
msgstr ""
"Dans le champ :guilabel:`Instructions`, saisissez une brève description de "
"la page en cours de création. Celle-ci doit inclure quelques mots-clés "
"importants qui définissent l'objectif et la portée de la page."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:78
msgid ""
"Select one of the tone options for the page, such "
"as :guilabel:`Concise`, :guilabel:`Professional`, :guilabel:`Friendly`, :guilabel:`Persuasive`, "
"or :guilabel:`Informative`."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez l'une des options de ton pour la page, telle que "
":guilabel:`Concis`, :guilabel:`Professionnel`, :guilabel:`Convivial`, "
":guilabel:`Persuasif` ou :guilabel:`Informatif`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create with AI`. It may take a few moments for the webpage "
"to load."
msgstr ""
"Cliquez sur :guilabel:`Créer avec l'IA`. Le chargement de la page web peut "
"prendre quelques instants."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:None
msgid "The new page pop-up window with the \"AI Generate text\" options."
msgstr ""
"La fenêtre contextuelle de nouvelle page avec les options « Générer du texte "
"avec l'IA »."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:88
msgid ""
"The AI application does **not** need to be installed on the database to use "
"the webpage generator."
msgstr ""
"L'application IA n'a **pas** besoin d'être installée sur la base de données "
"pour utiliser le générateur de page web."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:90
msgid ""
"Content created by the AI generator can be customized using "
"the :doc:`website editor <../web_design>`."
msgstr ""
"Le contenu créé par le générateur IA peut être personnalisé à l'aide de "
":doc:`l'éditeur de site web <../web_design>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:92
msgid "The AI webpage generator is not available for the *Blank* page type."
msgstr ""
"Le générateur de pages web IA n'est pas disponible pour le type de page "
"*Vierge*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:93
msgid ""
"The webpage generator may create :ref:`buttons <website/elements/buttons>`. "
"Before publishing the webpage, confirm that all buttons are linked to an "
"active webpage."
msgstr ""
"Le générateur de pages web peut créer des :ref:`boutons <website/elements/"
"buttons>`. Avant de publier la page web, vérifier que tous les boutons sont "
"liés à une page web active."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:97
msgid ":doc:`Web design <../web_design>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Conception web <../web_design>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:98
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/ai`"
