#~ "un blog, etc.) qui renvoie à votre propre site Web est également en "
#~ "\"dofollow\". "

#~ msgid ""
#~ "But every link posted by a contributor that links to an external website "
#~ "is \"nofollow\". In that way, you do not run the risk of people posting "
